00:03:47,525 --> 00:03:51,868
we are going from today to this bright and shiny future, we expect this lovely path of

72
00:03:51,908 --> 00:03:55,731
continuous improvement and getting everything better all of the time. I mean, the real fact

73
00:03:55,771 --> 00:03:59,374
is it actually looks a little bit more like this. The expectation that you bring something

74
00:03:59,434 --> 00:04:04,598
in and it will immediately cause your teams to feel a little bit uncomfortable and it

75
00:04:04,678 --> 00:04:08,320
is change and it is different. The habits that people formed before will no longer be

76
00:04:08,421 --> 00:04:09,662
useful when you go into this state.

77
00:04:11,047 --> 00:04:14,068
Going into the process, understanding that there's going to be an impact means that you

78
00:04:14,088 --> 00:04:17,489
can look for how to improve, how it's going to cause the improvement in the future.

79
00:04:17,889 --> 00:04:19,770
You can look for small wins and look for a turnaround.

